{"article_id":"VM40lLHbKcEFfwpz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"BUENOS AIRES , Argentina -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump said late Saturday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he will formally terminate the North American Free Trade Agreement soon , a move","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"designed to put pressure on Congress","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"to approve a new deal","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"he signed during the G-20 summit .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"\" I 'll be terminating it within a relatively short period of time , \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Trump told reporters aboard Air Force One","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"as he flew back to Washington after a two-day meeting in Argentina with the leaders of other major world economies .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"\" We ( will ) get rid of NAFTA .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"It 's been a disaster for the United States . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Trump signed a new deal here Friday with the president of Mexico and Canada ' s prime minister ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"following through on a campaign promise","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"he made","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to renegotiate the long controversial NAFTA agreement .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"The move will give Congress six months to accept that new agreement","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"or revert to pre-NAFTA trade rules .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The decision was intended to send a message to Democrats ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"who will take control of the House of Representatives in January .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Many have expressed skepticism about the new trade agreement","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"that Trump negotiated .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"The president ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"who cited the death of former President George H.W . Bush late Friday","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"in canceling a scheduled news conference in Buenos Aires ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"also told reporters","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that he would likely sign a short-term agreement","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"to keep the government open past a deadline Friday .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Work in Congress is likely to be suspended for much of this week for Bush ' s funeral .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"`` If","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"( lawmakers )","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"come ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"which they have ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"to talk about an extension","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"because of President Bush 's passing ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"I would absolutely consider it","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and probably give it , \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"The president also said","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"his administration is still working on a second meeting with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Trump said","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"he expected","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that meeting could take place early next year , potentially in January or February .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Asked whether he would ever host Kim in the U.S. ,","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"`` At some point , yeah . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":89,"left":0,"right":88,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":88,"left":64,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":62,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":54,"right":61,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":49,"right":53,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":49,"left":1,"right":48,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":48,"left":2,"right":47,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":47,"left":3,"right":46,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":46,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":51,"r